workflow License Audit
runner deepseek

agent audit-licenses
title Audit Licenses
prompt Read THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md and licenses/native-sdk-Apache-2.0.txt and licenses/IBM-Plex-OFL.txt. Look for missing attributions, license incompatibilities, or outdated terms. Write a short compliance summary.
after none

approval review-audit
title Review Audit
after audit-licenses
